reviews.text: It is all about sea food, mostly came from Japan. There are many types of restaurants and some play place and a sea food grocery shop. It may be a good place to fill up your desire and hunger for sea food. In the grocery, there are not only sea food but also beef, pork, chicken, snacks, dessert and even small toy and stationary. Worthy to drop at.
Excellent! Super fresh seafood expertly prepared
very good place. oyster and Japanese food tasted really good. recommended for couples or family to eat there.
Many restaurant there. The decoration is pretty.

reviews.text: 呢度係黃埔花園除咗美食坊之外一個比較大嘅日本食肆集中地，而且有價錢好合理嘅日本食品超級市場，又有俾小朋友玩嘅場地同活動。去過唔同嘅食肆，味道同服務都不錯。但好可惜，可能因為位置偏遠咗dd，人流唔多，有好幾間商舖同高級海鮮檔執笠咗。希望呢度可以撐得過去
好遺憾。踩入埔新村一條街就迷失方向 掂樣都去唔到九號水產。
地方大，場地好好行，貨品偏貴，基本真系賣海產及其副產品，可能黄埔本地及日藉居民接受岛呢级别嘅價錢，非一般消費層到逹。🙇我少食海產，
